{"data":[{"name":"112:1","price":"(நபியே!) கூறுவீராக! (வணங்கத் தகுதியான இறைவனாகிய) அல்லாஹ் ஒருவன்தான்.","arabic":"قُلۡ هُوَ ٱللَّهُ أَحَدٌ","category":["112 (Al-Ikhlas)","Al-Ikhlas","Surah Al-Ikhlas"],"ayahNumber":6222,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"qul huwa al-lahu aḥadun ","translations":["Say","He","(is) Allah","the One","(1)"],"transliterationArr":["qul","huwa","al-lahu","aḥadun",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,430],[2,430,700],[3,700,1680],[4,1680,2915]]}},{"name":"112:2","price":"அல்லாஹ்தான் நிறைவான தலைவன் (-எல்லா உயர் தகுதிகளையும் உடையவன், எக்குறையுமற்றவன், எல்லாப் படைப்புகளின் தேவைகளையும் நிறைவேற்றுகிறவன், எத்தேவையுமற்றவன், உண்மையானவன், நிறைவானவன்).","arabic":"ٱللَّهُ ٱلصَّمَدُ","category":["112 (Al-Ikhlas)","Al-Ikhlas","Surah Al-Ikhlas"],"ayahNumber":6223,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"al-lahu al-ṣamadu ","translations":["Allah","the Eternal, the Absolute","(2)"],"transliterationArr":["al-lahu","al-ṣamadu",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1050],[2,1050,2485]]}},{"name":"112:3","price":"(அவன் யாரையும்) பெற்றெடுக்கவில்லை. இன்னும், அவன் (யாராலும்) பெற்றெடுக்கப்படவுமில்லை. (ஆகவே, அவனுக்கு குழந்தையுமில்லை, தந்தையுமில்லை.)","arabic":"لَمۡ يَلِدۡ وَلَمۡ يُولَدۡ","category":["112 (Al-Ikhlas)","Al-Ikhlas","Surah Al-Ikhlas"],"ayahNumber":6224,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"lam yalid walam yūlad ","translations":["Not","He begets","and not","He is begotten","(3)"],"transliterationArr":["lam","yalid","walam","yūlad",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,430],[2,430,1050],[3,1050,1740],[4,1740,2915]]}},{"name":"112:4","price":"இன்னும், அவனுக்கு நிகராக ஒருவருமில்லை.","arabic":"وَلَمۡ يَكُن لَّهُۥ كُفُوًا أَحَدُۢ","category":["112 (Al-Ikhlas)","Al-Ikhlas","Surah Al-Ikhlas"],"ayahNumber":6225,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"walam yakun lahu kufuwan aḥadun ","translations":["And not","is","for Him","equivalent","any [one]","(4)"],"transliterationArr":["walam","yakun","lahu","kufuwan","aḥadun",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,530],[2,530,1250],[3,1250,2080],[4,2080,3000],[5,3000,4695]]}},{"name":"113:1","price":"(நபியே!) கூறுவீராக! அதிகாலையின் இறைவனிடம் பாதுகாப்புத் தேடுகிறேன்,","arabic":"قُلۡ أَعُوذُ بِرَبِّ ٱلۡفَلَقِ","category":["113 (Al-Falaq)","Al-Falaq","Surah Al-Falaq"],"ayahNumber":6226,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"qul aʿūdhu birabbi al-falaqi ","translations":["Say","I seek refuge","in (the) Lord","(of) the dawn","(1)"],"transliterationArr":["qul","aʿūdhu","birabbi","al-falaqi",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,360],[2,360,1280],[3,1280,2110],[4,2110,3005]]}},{"name":"113:2","price":"அவன் படைத்தவற்றின் தீங்கைவிட்டும்.","arabic":"مِن شَرِّ مَا خَلَقَ","category":["113 (Al-Falaq)","Al-Falaq","Surah Al-Falaq"],"ayahNumber":6227,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"min sharri mā khalaqa ","translations":["From","(the) evil","(of) what","He created","(2)"],"transliterationArr":["min","sharri","mā","khalaqa",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,940],[2,940,2040],[3,2040,2380],[4,2380,3595]]}},{"name":"113:3","price":"இன்னும், காரிருள் படரும்போது இரவின் தீங்கை விட்டும்,","arabic":"وَمِن شَرِّ غَاسِقٍ إِذَا وَقَبَ","category":["113 (Al-Falaq)","Al-Falaq","Surah Al-Falaq"],"ayahNumber":6228,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"wamin sharri ghāsiqin idhā waqaba ","translations":["And from","(the) evil","(of) darkness","when","it spreads","(3)"],"transliterationArr":["wamin","sharri","ghāsiqin","idhā","waqaba",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,740],[2,740,2140],[3,2140,3250],[4,3250,3870],[5,3870,4945]]}},{"name":"113:4","price":"இன்னும், முடிச்சுகளில் ஊதுகிற சூனியக்காரிகளின் தீங்கை விட்டும்,","arabic":"وَمِن شَرِّ ٱلنَّفَّٰثَٰتِ فِي ٱلۡعُقَدِ","category":["113 (Al-Falaq)","Al-Falaq","Surah Al-Falaq"],"ayahNumber":6229,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"wamin sharri al-nafāthāti fī al-ʿuqadi ","translations":["And from","(the) evil","(of) the blowers","in","the knots","(4)"],"transliterationArr":["wamin","sharri","al-nafāthāti","fī","al-ʿuqadi",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1410],[2,1410,2150],[3,2150,4440],[4,4440,4630],[5,4630,5935]]}},{"name":"113:5","price":"பொறாமைக்காரன் பொறாமைப்படும்போது, (அந்த) பொறாமைக்காரனின் தீங்கை விட்டும் (பாதுகாப்புத் தேடுகிறேன்).","arabic":"وَمِن شَرِّ حَاسِدٍ إِذَا حَسَدَ","category":["113 (Al-Falaq)","Al-Falaq","Surah Al-Falaq"],"ayahNumber":6230,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"wamin sharri ḥāsidin idhā ḥasada ","translations":["And from","(the) evil","(of) an envier","when","he envies","(5)"],"transliterationArr":["wamin","sharri","ḥāsidin","idhā","ḥasada",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,500],[2,500,1990],[3,1990,3160],[4,3160,3750],[5,3750,5605]]}},{"name":"114:1","price":"(நபியே!) கூறுவீராக! மக்களின் இறைவனிடம் பாதுகாப்புத் தேடுகிறேன்.","arabic":"قُلۡ أَعُوذُ بِرَبِّ ٱلنَّاسِ","category":["114 (An-Nas)","An-Nas","Surah An-Nas"],"ayahNumber":6231,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"qul aʿūdhu birabbi al-nāsi ","translations":["Say","I seek refuge","in (the) Lord","(of) mankind","(1)"],"transliterationArr":["qul","aʿūdhu","birabbi","al-nāsi",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,330],[2,330,1230],[3,1230,2050],[4,2050,6085]]}},{"name":"114:2","price":"மக்களின் அரசன்,","arabic":"مَلِكِ ٱلنَّاسِ","category":["114 (An-Nas)","An-Nas","Surah An-Nas"],"ayahNumber":6232,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"maliki al-nāsi ","translations":["(The) King","(of) mankind","(2)"],"transliterationArr":["maliki","al-nāsi",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,640],[2,640,5205]]}},{"name":"114:3","price":"மக்களின் வணக்கத்திற்குரியவன்,","arabic":"إِلَٰهِ ٱلنَّاسِ","category":["114 (An-Nas)","An-Nas","Surah An-Nas"],"ayahNumber":6233,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"ilāhi al-nāsi ","translations":["(The) God","(of) mankind","(3)"],"transliterationArr":["ilāhi","al-nāsi",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,840],[2,840,5295]]}},{"name":"114:4","price":"வீணான மனக்குழப்பங்களை, சந்தேகங்களை ஏற்படுத்தக்கூடியவன், (அல்லாஹ்வின் பெயரைக் கூறும்போது) மறைந்துவிடக் கூடியவனின் தீங்கை விட்டும் (பாதுகாப்புத் தேடுகிறேன்).","arabic":"مِن شَرِّ ٱلۡوَسۡوَاسِ ٱلۡخَنَّاسِ","category":["114 (An-Nas)","An-Nas","Surah An-Nas"],"ayahNumber":6234,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"min sharri al-waswāsi al-khanāsi ","translations":["From","(the) evil","(of) the whisperer","the one who withdraws","(4)"],"transliterationArr":["min","sharri","al-waswāsi","al-khanāsi",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,400],[2,400,2119],[3,2119,3389],[4,3389,7914]]}},{"name":"114:5","price":"அவன் மக்களுடைய நெஞ்சங்களில் வீண் எண்ணங்களை ஏற்படுத்துகிறான்.","arabic":"ٱلَّذِي يُوَسۡوِسُ فِي صُدُورِ ٱلنَّاسِ","category":["114 (An-Nas)","An-Nas","Surah An-Nas"],"ayahNumber":6235,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"alladhī yuwaswisu fī ṣudūri al-nāsi ","translations":["The one who","whispers","in","(the) breasts","(of) mankind","(5)"],"transliterationArr":["alladhī","yuwaswisu","fī","ṣudūri","al-nāsi",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1140],[2,1140,2130],[3,2130,2510],[4,2510,3420],[5,3420,7865]]}},{"name":"114:6","price":"(குழப்பங்களை ஏற்படுத்துகிற அவன்) ஜின் இனத்திலும் இருக்கிறான். இன்னும், மனித இனத்திலும் இருக்கிறான்.","arabic":"مِنَ ٱلۡجِنَّةِ وَٱلنَّاسِ","category":["114 (An-Nas)","An-Nas","Surah An-Nas"],"ayahNumber":6236,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"mina al-jinati wal-nāsi ","translations":["From","the jinn","and men","(6)"],"transliterationArr":["mina","al-jinati","wal-nāsi",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,380],[2,380,2610],[3,2610,8185]]}},{"name":"109:1","price":"(நபியே!) கூறுவீராக: நிராகரிப்பாளர்களே!","arabic":"قُلۡ يَٰٓأَيُّهَا ٱلۡكَٰفِرُونَ","category":["109 (Al-Kafirun)","Al-Kafirun","Surah Al-Kafirun"],"ayahNumber":6208,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"qul yāayyuhā al-kāfirūna ","translations":["Say","O","disbelievers","(1)"],"transliterationArr":["qul","yāayyuhā","al-kāfirūna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,400],[2,400,3370],[3,3370,7425]]}},{"name":"109:2","price":"நீங்கள் வணங்குவதை நான் வணங்க மாட்டேன்.","arabic":"لَآ أَعۡبُدُ مَا تَعۡبُدُونَ","category":["109 (Al-Kafirun)","Al-Kafirun","Surah Al-Kafirun"],"ayahNumber":6209,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"lā aʿbudu mā taʿbudūna ","translations":["Not","I worship","what","you worship","(2)"],"transliterationArr":["lā","aʿbudu","mā","taʿbudūna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,2590],[2,2590,3460],[3,3460,3840],[4,3840,7365]]}},{"name":"109:3","price":"இன்னும், நான் வணங்குகிறவனை நீங்கள் வணங்குபவர்களாக இல்லை.","arabic":"وَلَآ أَنتُمۡ عَٰبِدُونَ مَآ أَعۡبُدُ","category":["109 (Al-Kafirun)","Al-Kafirun","Surah Al-Kafirun"],"ayahNumber":6210,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"walā antum ʿābidūna mā aʿbudu ","translations":["And not","you","(are) worshippers","(of) what","I worship","(3)"],"transliterationArr":["walā","antum","ʿābidūna","mā","aʿbudu",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,2380],[2,2380,3760],[3,3760,5090],[4,5090,6920],[5,6920,8155]]}},{"name":"109:4","price":"இன்னும், நீங்கள் வணங்கியதை நான் வணங்குபவனாக இல்லை.","arabic":"وَلَآ أَنَا۠ عَابِدٞ مَّا عَبَدتُّمۡ","category":["109 (Al-Kafirun)","Al-Kafirun","Surah Al-Kafirun"],"ayahNumber":6211,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"walā anā ʿābidun mā ʿabadttum ","translations":["And not","I am","a worshipper","(of) what","you worship","(4)"],"transliterationArr":["walā","anā","ʿābidun","mā","ʿabadttum",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,2320],[2,2320,2700],[3,2700,3630],[4,3630,4990],[5,4990,6325]]}},{"name":"109:5","price":"இன்னும், நான் வணங்குகிறவனை நீங்கள் வணங்குபவர்களாக இல்லை.","arabic":"وَلَآ أَنتُمۡ عَٰبِدُونَ مَآ أَعۡبُدُ","category":["109 (Al-Kafirun)","Al-Kafirun","Surah Al-Kafirun"],"ayahNumber":6212,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"walā antum ʿābidūna mā aʿbudu ","translations":["And not","you","(are) worshippers","(of) what","I worship","(5)"],"transliterationArr":["walā","antum","ʿābidūna","mā","aʿbudu",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,2120],[2,2120,3780],[3,3780,5230],[4,5230,7070],[5,7070,8365]]}},{"name":"109:6","price":"உங்கள் (வழிபாடுகளுக்குரிய) கூலி உங்களுக்குக் கிடைக்கும். இன்னும், எனது (வழிபாடுகளுக்குரிய) கூலி எனக்குக் கிடைக்கும்.","arabic":"لَكُمۡ دِينُكُمۡ وَلِيَ دِينِ","category":["109 (Al-Kafirun)","Al-Kafirun","Surah Al-Kafirun"],"ayahNumber":6213,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"lakum dīnukum waliya dīni ","translations":["For you","(is) your religion","and for me","(is) my religion","(6)"],"transliterationArr":["lakum","dīnukum","waliya","dīni",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,590],[2,590,1720],[3,1720,2510],[4,2510,5465]]}}],"dua":{"id":2,"name":"Four Quls (Al-Arba' Qul)","arabicName":"الأربع قل","reference":"112:1-4, 113:1-5, 114:1-6, 109:1-6","verseTitle":"The Four Declarations of Divine Oneness and Protection","significanceReason":"Considered a complete spiritual protection and declaration of divine unity, represent spiritual protection, affirmation of divine oneness, rejection of polytheism, and seeking refuge from all forms of harm, recited for spiritual defense, mental peace, and as a comprehensive protection against negative energies, jealousy, and spiritual afflictions."},"version":{"key":"tamil_omar","direction":"ltr","language_iso_code":"ta","version":"1.0.2","last_update":1670915064,"title":"Tamil Translation - Omar Sharif","description":"Translation of the Quran meanings into Tamil by Sh. Omar Sharif ibn Abdusalam"}}